{"tid":1259521,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［26/6］係愛丁堡廣場遇到天使","createTime":"2019-06-26T15:04:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T15:39:06.000Z","uid":29230,"like":35,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e46e444347629258a153357b274f59ef8ca51e7e","tid":1259521,"uid":29230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:04:01.000Z","msg":"今日我返煙腸<br />\n所以著左shirt衫<br />\n入面又打左個底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己又on9無帶衫換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n67點左右自己一個人坐左係moon前<br />\n之後開始多人個時feel到好鬼熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拎左民陣張野起勢咁撥<br />\n點知隔離個女仔笑住咁借左個風扇仔俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢個笑容好甜 把聲好溫柔<br />\n個下先發覺支持民主既香港女仔原來咁高汁<br />\n<br />\n咁自己吹左陣啦<br />\n見佢又好攰咁 dup低頭<br />\n就用風扇仔對住佢吹（因為真係唔好意思）<br />\n但係佢叫我自己吹啦 佢唔熱<br />\n我臨走前問佢飲唔飲野<br />\n想買支/杯野飲俾佢報答佢<br />\n點知佢又話唔洗 <br />\n佢真係好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但應該唔會再見到<br />\n只係想講香港仲有好多好女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e93e54b1dad13e3edcbcfed958e68ad7391376e","tid":1259521,"uid":29230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:07:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abdfeccc58702ff75af6e721fb53fb40d9008482","tid":1259521,"uid":29230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:16:25.000Z","msg":"毒撚開po無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nd人突然去狗會<br />\n去返狗會po叫人唔好沖<br />\n唔好理呢個po啦<br />\n由呢個自己po沉"},{"pid":"465051f996ac2ae4ae51597b72e12b279d54ff1a","tid":1259521,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:18:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 回吓啦咁我"},{"pid":"dd08375a27ff05a96c3fb32a4d1bcfb3082bb0c8","tid":1259521,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:19:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a1028dad9a2396fc27a01e0f6a1240c0e8aa32a","tid":1259521,"uid":232671,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:20:13.000Z","msg":"幫你推下post喇.."},{"pid":"102cadd8f4b4a42d310459a155c35eff899ff2ba","tid":1259521,"uid":16181,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:21:01.000Z","msg":"有男朋友就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n參與集會主要目的唔係為左識男女朋友～"},{"pid":"20a1a6dc1824209ff526e35b9663ab9735dd2d1f","tid":1259521,"uid":29230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"465051f996ac2ae4ae51597b72e12b279d54ff1a","tid":1259521,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:18:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 回吓啦咁我"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:22:12.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9549f89af1bee3b7e34ae8707b4daeedc0b32f3c","tid":1259521,"uid":29230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd08375a27ff05a96c3fb32a4d1bcfb3082bb0c8","tid":1259521,"uid":3028